Message.message: Once upon a time, five tiny adorable fairies happened upon a hollow in a great old tree.
The smallest and most fearful of the fairies peered inside, but was too afraid to go in.
The other four, who were more curious and adventurous, entered the tree. This left the little fairy all alone.
She waited and waited, but her friends didn't return. Mustering her courage, she ventured in after them.
You see, the brave little fairy didn't know about -me-.
Watch out for my web little fairy. It's easy to get stuck.
Don't worry. Like all the best fairy tales, this one has a happy ending.
The brave little fairy finds her friends.
And she'll never be apart from them again.
